				<p class="text-black text-center font-sans text-[15px] font-normal leading-6 sm:text-[32px] sm:font-medium sm:leading-[42px]">
					An innovative profit strategist, respected business advisor<br class="hidden sm:block">and sought-after speaker, Peter's work is guided by one core belief: <strong class="font-bold">lifting profit comes from thinking differently,<br class="hidden sm:block">not from doing more.</strong>
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="max-w-[945px] mx-auto mb-10">
				<h2 class="text-black text-center font-sans text-xl font-bold leading-9 sm:text-4xl sm:leading-[48px]">Your success drives his.</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="max-w-[945px] mx-auto mb-10">
				<p class="text-black text-center font-sans text-[15px] font-normal leading-6 sm:text-[32px] sm:font-medium sm:leading-[42px]">
					Peter works with entrepreneurs, executives, and leadership teams willing to challenge assumptions, uncover blind spots, and embrace the counterintuitive thinking needed to achieve greater profitability, growth, and staying power.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="max-w-[945px] mx-auto mb-6">
				<p class="text-black text-center font-sans text-[15px] font-normal leading-6 sm:text-[32px] sm:font-medium sm:leading-[42px]">
					His first book, <a href="https://a.co/d/060pFnZ5" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-black no-underline hover:underline"><em class="italic font-bold underline">Mind Shift. Profit Lift.</em></a>, quickly climbed <br class="hidden sm:block">Amazon's new release rankings across multiple categories,<br class="hidden sm:block">including entrepreneurship, retail business, and hospitality.
				</p>
